description:
Officer Jenny is part of the local police force in the Alola Region. Each island and area has a Jenny who looks exactly the same as she does elsewhere in the Alola region though they do look different compared to their Jenny counterparts elsewhere in the Pokémon World.
The most noticeable different between Alola region Jenny and those from elsewhere in the Pokémon World is their haircut and that she wears a bullet proof jacket.
name: Junsaa
